604
00:37:59,528 --> 00:38:01,360
[Yingzhou Governor Mo Qianzhi]

605
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:03,120
I am Mo Qianzhi.

606
00:38:03,120 --> 00:38:05,160
Apologies for not

607
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:08,424
welcoming you properly.

608
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:13,000
Governor Mo.

609
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,800
